<body>
	<section class="level-report" id="container" data-init="share">
		<section class="user-top">
			<dl class="user-cont">
				<dt>
					<section class="user-img">
						<img src="<%= imagessrc%>user.jpg" alt="">
					</section>
					<p>Robert</p>
				</dt>
				<dd>Dear,smith<br>What a nice student! Your lovely nice singing will surely hepi you learn willy English singing good well.</dd>
			</dl>
		</section>
		<section class="level">
			<section class="level-n">
				<img src="<%= imagessrc%>l_1.png" alt="">
			</section>
			<h3 class="level-tit">G2 Early Reading</h3>
			<section class="level-item">
				<h3>课程目标</h3>
				<p>将 Phonics 技能实际使用到阅读中，外教通过词汇、短语和句子中的讲解以及丰富多样的教学形式，引领孩子从分享阅读过度到自主阅读，确保孩子具备一定的词汇量，能够进行最初的创造性写作，同时确保听说水平在阅读的带动下获得进一步的提升。</p>
			</section>
			<section class="level-item">
				<h3>课程重点</h3>
				<p>开始阅读、强化听说、获取知识。</p>
			</section>
		</section>
		<section class="skills">
			<h3 class="skills-tit"><img src="<%= imagessrc%>analysis.png" alt=""></h3>
			<ul class="skill-list">
				<li>
					<h3 class="a-tit"><img src="<%= imagessrc%>a_tit1.png" alt=""></h3>
					<section class="a-score">
						<span class="color-y">1</span>
						<span class="color-y">2</span>
						<span>3</span>
						<span>4</span>
						<span>5</span>
					</section>
					<p>有较多单词出现误读和发音错误</p>
					<span class="score"><em>2</em>分</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h3 class="a-tit"><img src="<%= imagessrc%>a_tit2.png" alt=""></h3>
					<section class="a-score">
						<span class="color-y">1</span>
						<span class="color-y">2</span>
						<span>3</span>
						<span>4</span>
						<span>5</span>
					</section>
					<p>出现某些特定的语法错误或复杂的句型使用上的错误。</p>
					<span class="score"><em>2</em>分</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h3 class="a-tit"><img src="<%= imagessrc%>a_tit3.png" alt=""></h3>
					<section class="a-score">
						<span class="color-y">1</span>
						<span class="color-y">2</span>
						<span>3</span>
						<span>4</span>
						<span>5</span>
					</section>
					<p>有时词汇使用已出现错误不够精准地道。</p>
					<span class="score"><em>2</em>分</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h3 class="a-tit"><img src="<%= imagessrc%>a_tit4.png" alt=""></h3>
					<section class="a-score">
						<span class="color-y">1</span>
						<span class="color-y">2</span>
						<span>3</span>
						<span>4</span>
						<span>5</span>
					</section>
					<p>进行复杂交流时，表达不够流畅，逻辑性和连贯性较低。</p>
					<span class="score"><em>2</em>分</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h3 class="a-tit"><img src="<%= imagessrc%>a_tit5.png" alt=""></h3>
					<section class="a-score">
						<span class="color-y">1</span>
						<span class="color-y">2</span>
						<span>3</span>
						<span>4</span>
						<span>5</span>
					</section>
					<p>当语速较快，生僻词较多，语法结构复杂，话题不熟悉的情况下存在理上的偏差。</p>
					<span class="score"><em>2</em>分</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
		<section class="lesson">
			<h3 class="skills-tit"><img src="<%= imagessrc%>analysis.png" alt=""></h3>
			<ul class="lesson-list">
				<li class="color1">
					<h3 class="l-tit"><span>3</span>个需要注意的发音 <i></i></h3>
					<p>Climb 攀爬 /klɑɪm/ friend 朋友 /frend/ Animal 动物 / æn.ɪ.məl/  </p>
				</li>
				<li class="color2">
					<h3 class="l-tit"><span>6</span>个新单词需要学习<i></i></h3>
					<p>duck   pig   cow   cat   horse   dog </p>
				</li>
				<li class="color3">
					<h3 class="l-tit"><span>2</span>个句子需要掌握<i></i></h3>
					<p>Who is she? <br>  She is my mother.</p>
				</li>
				<li class="color4">
					<h3 class="l-tit"><span>1</span>首歌谣可以学唱<i></i></h3>
					<p>The bear went over the mountain.</p>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
		<section class="bottom">
			<img src="<%= imagessrc%>very_good.jpg" alt="">
			<p><a href="javascript:;">下一步</a></p>
		</section>
	</section>
</body>
